author: Warhammer
description:
Raising high his storm shield, Rampart, as he swings the Fist of Dorn, this epic hero wades through his foes like a warship smashing through stormy seas. Tune in to this paint guide to learn everything you need to know about painting Chapter Master Darnath Lysander!

Here’s a list of the paints we used in today’s video:

Base:
Abaddon Black
Corax White
Iron Warriors
Khorne Red
Mephiston Red
Rhinox Hide
Screamer Pink

Layer:
Canoptek Alloy
Doombull Brown
Dorn Yellow
Evil Sunz Scarlet
Flash Gitz Yellow 
Flayed One Flesh
Pink Horror
Screaming Skull
Stormhost Silver
Stormvermin Fur
Wild Rider Red

Contrast:
Aethermatic Blue
Imperial Fist 

Shade:
Casandora Yellow
Targor Rageshade

Extra:
L Base
L Shade
Lahmian Medium
M Base
M Shade
S Base
S Dry
S Layer

If you enjoyed this and want to learn more, our YouTube channel has an array of beginner-friendly videos to get you started.

Follow for more Warhammer, more often:

- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/warhammerofficial/
- Threads: http
title: How To Paint Darnath Lysander of the Imperial Fists | Warhammer 40,000
